text: Baulne-en-Brie is a former commune. It is in the Hauts-de-France region in the Aisne department in the north of France. In 2012, 262 people lived there. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune Vallées-en-Champagne.Arrêté préfectoral 23 November 2015 ==References== Category:Former communes in Aisne
title: Baulne-en-Brie
